                                    </extent>
                                    <foliation>
                                        <locus from="1" to="328" scheme="folios"/> medieval foliation in black ink. Errors in foliation: 1-135, 137-191, 191a, 192-225, 227-251, 251a, 252-329. </foliation>
                                    <condition>Parchment stained and dirty in places, e.g. <locus from="19r" to="19r" scheme="folios"/>. Holes and tears in the parchment in places, some of which show signs of contemporary repairs, e.g. <locus from="141" to="141" scheme="folios"/> and <locus from="202" to="202" scheme="folios"/>. <locus from="136" to="136" scheme="folios"/> cut out, only stub remains.</condition>
                                </supportDesc>
